descript.abstract: This line dataset contains height values for selected parts of selected contours in Horse Cave, KY.
descript.purpose: This data is derived from USGS DLG Hypsography data. It is intended to be used to demonstrate the construction of a TIN surface using various vector data sources.

procstep.procdesc: The data was generalized to eliminate vertices, converted to shapefile, clipped, and most of the contours were deleted. A few contours were left to illustrate adding breaklines to a TIN.

dataqual.complete: incomplete. This data was clipped and a few contours were selected solely to illustrate the use of linear features for adding hard breaklines to a TIN.
